1
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:12,400
On the night of the murder,

2
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:14,160
you were at the scene.

3
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:15,080
What did you see?

4
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:15,920
Inspector,

5
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:17,680
at the time, I heard some

6
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:18,840
strange noises.

7
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:20,600
Who's there?

8
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:23,760
Who's playing tricks?

9
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:35,240
Murder!

10
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:36,640
Murder!

11
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:41,440
I also saw a figure from behind

12
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:42,800
that looked like Lord Guan.

13
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:45,200
Are you sure you saw Lord Guan's back?

14
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,320
I'm sure.

15
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,040
That build,

16
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:49,440
that appearance,

17
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,480
it was exactly like Lord Guan

18
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:53,320
on the stage!

19
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:57,480
On the day of the murder,

20
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,800
did anything strange happen?

21
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,840
That day was just like any other.

22
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:03,800
Nothing strange happened.

23
00:02:05,440 --> 00:02:05,760
However,

24
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:06,880
in the theater,

25
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,480
Lord Guan's costume went missing.

26
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,480
I looked for it for a long time but couldn't find it.

27
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:15,560
That day,

28
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,480
when I passed by the Buddhist hall,

29
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,000
I accidentally

30
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:21,280
saw Boss Mei and Brother Bao struggling.

31
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:22,800
They were arguing loudly.

32
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:23,800
Let go of me!

33
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,840
I didn't dare to stay long,

34
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,080
so I left quickly.

35
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:28,920
As for what happened

36
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:30,920
after that,

37
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:32,120
I really don't know.

38
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:33,640
What were they arguing about?

39
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:36,840
I was too far away,

40
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:37,720
so I didn't hear clearly.

41
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:40,000
I only heard Brother Bao sounding very fierce,

42
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:41,840
and Boss Mei seemed very angry.

43
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:44,280
So that day,

44
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:46,360
the poison put in Brother Bao's teacup,

45
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,560
was it Xiao Yuejiao who did it?

46
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:49,560
Yes.

47
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:50,640
But Sister Yuejiao

48
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:52,080
didn't want to poison Boss Mei to death.

49
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:54,360
She just wanted to ruin her voice

50
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:57,000
so she could take back control of the theater.

51
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:02,360
You guys go back first.

52
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:03,640
If you find any evidence,

53
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:04,840
let me know immediately.

54
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,440
Understood.

55
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,440
Mei Yanhong, you witch!

56
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:11,440
You must have killed my man!

57
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,280
Give me back my man!

58
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,160
Mei Yanhong!

59
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,280
Mrs. Bao!

60
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:16,800
Mei Yanhong!

61
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:19,120
She is the murderer who killed my man!

62
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:22,520
Why did you let her go?

63
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,960
Mrs. Bao, calm down.

64
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,400
The police bureau needs evidence to arrest someone.

65
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:27,680
Besides, Boss Mei

66
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,680
has no motive to kill Brother Bao.

67
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:33,600
She caused my man to get food poisoning

68
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:35,680
and lose his voice.

69
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:38,280
Because she didn't want to pay compensation,

70
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,440
she killed him!

71
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:42,840
Isn't that a motive?

72
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,520
Don't talk nonsense.

73
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,800
Boss Mei is not that kind of person.

74
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:48,400
Why not?

75
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:50,680
She usually uses singing as an excuse

76
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:51,800
to seduce my man.

77
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:53,440
Because she didn't want to pay,

78
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,720
and failed to seduce him,

79
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:57,400
she killed him out of anger and shame!

80
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:58,800
Stop talking nonsense!

81
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,000
I didn't seduce him,

82
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,320
and I certainly didn't kill him!

83
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:05,120
It was clearly Brother Bao himself

84
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,000
who didn't behave properly

85
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:07,720
and almost assaulted Boss Mei!

86
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,560
And you're here twisting the truth

87
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,320
and ruining her reputation!

88
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,560
Your whole family,

89
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:12,880
you guys are just darn it!

90
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,560
I see.

91
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,280
I see.

92
00:04:21,520 --> 00:04:23,240
You're her lover too, aren't you?

93
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,040
Let me tell you.

94
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,560
She's a jinx.

95
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,800
She's a reincarnated fox spirit.

96
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:31,560
She's a menace.

97
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,520
Fox spirit!

98
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,000
I'll kill you!

99
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:34,720
Hey!

100
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:35,600
Mrs. Bao!

101
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:38,440
You've all been fooled by her!

102
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,720
She's a witch!

103
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,440
Just a witch!

104
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:42,000
Witch!

105
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:42,840
Mrs. Bao!

106
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:45,600
Mrs. Bao!

107
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:47,720
Mrs. Bao!

108
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:50,840
Hurry!

109
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:51,840
Take her to the hospital!

110
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:52,440
Yes, sir!

111
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:04,000
What a pity.

112
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,320
What a pity.

113
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,120
Boss Mei

114
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,560
is a genius in the opera world.

115
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:11,400
Her singing,

116
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:12,000
acting,

117
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:12,520
and stage presence

118
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:13,560
are all spectacular.

119
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,280
Whether playing a female role

120
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:15,960
or a red-faced male role,

121
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:17,000
she is absolutely unmatched.

122
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,400
From now on,

123
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:19,800
we'll never hear

124
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,280
Boss Mei's opera again.

125
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:23,840
So,

126
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,240
tonight's farewell performance,

127
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,440
I absolutely cannot miss it.

128
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,240
Then let's all go tonight

129
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,680
and see if this Lord Guan

130
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,360
will manifest his power.

131
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,160
Lord Guan.

132
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,040
Bravo!

133
00:05:59,040 --> 00:05:59,760
Bravo!

134
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,000
Bravo!

135
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:01,960
Bravo!

136
00:06:01,960 --> 00:06:02,560
Bravo!

137
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,160
Bravo!

138
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,920
Bravo!

139
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,040
Bravo!

140
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,480
Excellent, Boss Mei!

141
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,000
Mei Yanhong!

142
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:26,800
I'll kill you to avenge my husband!

143
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:28,000
I'll kill you!

144
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:37,480
Kill!

145
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:38,680
Mei Yanhong!

146
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:39,720
I'll kill you!

147
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,240
Kill!

148
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,360
Mei Yanhong!

149
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,560
I'll kill you!

150
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,040
Kill!

151
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:43,920
You must be startled, Boss Mei.

152
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:45,040
Mrs. Bao's health

153
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:45,920
seems to be unwell.

154
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,160
We have to take her

155
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,120
to the hospital first.

156
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,240
Inspector Huang.

157
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:50,600
Could you do me a favor?

158
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:52,360
Go ahead.

159
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:54,600
Uncle Qin.

160
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,040
Yes.

161
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,360
Give Mrs. Bao some money.

162
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,120
Mrs. Bao is also a pitiful person.

163
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,160
It's all because she lost her family

164
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:01,800
that she's like this.

165
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:04,640
Yes.

166
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,160
Okay.

167
00:07:09,840 --> 00:07:10,560
Inspector!

168
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:16,600
Kill!

169
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:17,800
Kill!

170
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:19,160
Kill!

171
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:27,840
Mei Yanhong!

172
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,600
I want you to pay with your life!

173
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,600
I'll kill you!

174
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,800
Give me back my man!

175
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,720
I'll kill you!

176
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:35,920
Give me back my man!

177
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:36,840
I'll kill you!

178
00:07:36,840 --> 00:07:37,680
I want revenge!

179
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,160
Stop pacing.

180
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,240
Stop pacing.

181
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,480
You walking back and forth like this...

182
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:00,680
...is making me dizzy.

183
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,680
You took Mrs. Bao to the hospital yesterday.

184
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,360
After you came back,

185
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,480
you've been acting really weird.

186
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,680
What exactly is bothering you?

187
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,440
Just tell me.

188
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,800
If something's wrong, say it out loud.

189
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,160
We can figure it out together.

190
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,240
You're always like this.

191
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:21,360
Keeping everything bottled up inside.

192
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,120
Hey.

193
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,040
I'm leaving.

194
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,240
Mrs. Bao...

195
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,040
...is dead.

196
00:08:40,160 --> 00:08:41,600
This is too bizarre.

197
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,240
Last night, we...

198
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,560
...clearly saw with our own eyes...

199
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:45,840
...Mrs. Bao being admitted to the ward.

200
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:48,360
It's only been one night,

201
00:08:48,680 --> 00:08:49,920
and she suddenly died in...

202
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:51,720
...such a remote alley.

203
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:54,680
Mrs. Bao...

204
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:55,800
...was struck by the same sharp weapon...

205
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:57,360
...that severed her carotid artery.

206
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:58,560
She died from excessive blood loss.

207
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,680
Based on the shape of the wound,

208
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:01,680
we can confirm...

209
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:02,800
...that it should be...

210
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,040
...the one used to kill Brother Bao and Xiao Yuejiao.

211
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:04,720
That murder weapon...

212
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,040
...is the exact same one.

213
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:10,040
Was it the Guan Dao again?

214
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:12,920
Could it be...

215
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,840
...that Lord Guan is out killing again?

216
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,040
Today,

217
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,680
is Boss Mei leaving the theater?

218
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:22,360
Yes.

219
00:09:22,920 --> 00:09:23,240
Good.

220
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,680
Let's go find Lord Guan.

221
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:43,800
Uncle Qin,

222
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:44,920
let's go.

223
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:46,480
Alright.

224
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:55,560
Inspector Huang.

225
00:09:55,680 --> 00:09:56,560
Why are you here?

226
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:57,320
Boss Mei.

227
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:58,680
Early this morning,

228
00:09:59,040 --> 00:10:00,280
someone in a remote alley...

229
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,200
...found the body of Mrs. Bao.
